title: HPE 3PAR: Remote Copy Groups
agents: 3par
catalog: hw/storagehw/hpe
license: GPL
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This check shows general information about the replication status of the
 remote copy group. The check will be {CRIT} if the remote copy mode is "STOPPED". Also
 the check will be {CRIT} if the device reports a status of INVALID, STOPPED or FAILSAFE
 and {WARN} for STARTING, RESTART, BACKUP or LOGGING. These states are configurable
 except for the remote copy group mode.

inventory:
 One service per group is created
